 Player of the Year: [[Christian McCaffrey]], Stanford\n*Pat Tillman Defensive Player of the Year: [[DeForest Buckner]], Oregon\n*Offensive Freshman of the Year: [[Josh Rosen]], UCLA\n*Defensive Freshman of the Year: [[Cameron Smith (American football)|Cameron Smith]], USC\n*Coach of the Year: [[Mike Leach (American football coach)|Mike Leach]], Washington State; [[David Shaw (American football)|David Shaw]], Stanford\n\n===All-Conference teams===\nThe following players earned [[List of All-Pac-12 Conference football teams|All-Pac-12]] honors.<ref>{{cite web|title=Pac-12 football all-Conference team announced |date=December 1, 2015 |publisher=Pac-12 Conference |url=http://pac-12.com/article/2015/12/01/pac-12-football-all-conference-team-announced |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6dTJyd51G?url=http://pac-12.com/article/2015/12/01/pac-12-football-all-conference-team-announced |archivedate=December 2, 2015 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n'''Offense:'''\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! colspan=\"4\" | <center>First Team</center>\n! colspan=\"4\" | <center>Second Team</center>\n|-\n!Pos.\n!Name\n!Yr.\n!School\n!Name\n!Yr.\n!School\n|-\n|QB || [[Luke Falk]] || So. || [[2015 Washington State Cougars football team|Washington State]] || [[Kevin Hogan]] || Sr. || [[2015 Stanford Cardinal football team|Stanford]]\n|- \n|QB || [[Jared Goff]] || Jr. || [[2015 California Golden Bears football team|California]] || {{BLACK}} || {{BLACK}} || {{BLACK}}\n|-\n|RB || [[Royce Freeman]] || So. || [[2015 Oregon Ducks football team|Oregon]] || [[Devontae Booker]] || Sr. || [[2015 Utah Utes football team|Utah]]\n|-\n|RB || [[Christian McCaffrey]] || So. || [[2015 Stanford Cardinal football team|Stanford]] || [[Paul Perkins]] || Jr. || [[2015 UCLA Bruins football team|UCLA]]\n|-\n|WR || [[Kenny Lawler]] || Jr. || [[2015 California Golden Bears football team|California]] || [[Bralon Addison]] || Jr. || [[2015 Oregon Ducks football team|Oregon]]\n|-\n|WR || [[Gabe Marks]] || Jr. || [[2015 Washing